I just ate a cob of corn.

882
00:36:23,147 --> 00:36:23,814
I'm full.

883
00:36:24,916 --> 00:36:25,716
I've trained

884
00:36:25,750 --> 00:36:26,751
several groups of young nurses.

885
00:36:27,485 --> 00:36:28,052
How come none of them

886
00:36:28,085 --> 00:36:29,053
is this considerate?

887
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:30,922
I should make them learn from him.

888
00:36:34,992 --> 00:36:35,693
Have a bowl, Sister Beibei.

889
00:36:36,093 --> 00:36:36,627
It's delicious.

890
00:36:38,362 --> 00:36:39,664
A card game with friends from Europe.

891
00:36:39,797 --> 00:36:41,365
Requesting permission from the boss to come home late.

892
00:36:41,465 --> 00:36:42,366
How could it not taste good?

893
00:36:43,668 --> 00:36:44,535
All right. You two eat.

894
00:36:56,147 --> 00:36:56,814
Good, right, Professor Fang?

895
00:36:57,682 --> 00:36:58,249
Very good.

896
00:37:01,118 --> 00:37:01,485
Reporting:

897
00:37:01,786 --> 00:37:02,253
five cards.

898
00:37:03,287 --> 00:37:03,754
Xiao Lin,

899
00:37:04,522 --> 00:37:04,956
your turn.

900
00:37:05,289 --> 00:37:05,590
Okay.

901
00:37:06,724 --> 00:37:07,325
How many cards does Director Sheng have?

902
00:37:07,558 --> 00:37:08,025
Two.

903
00:37:12,530 --> 00:37:13,130
Play a six.

904
00:37:14,732 --> 00:37:15,533
Why not play something bigger?

905
00:37:17,635 --> 00:37:18,769
There are no bombs left, right?

906
00:37:20,571 --> 00:37:20,838
None, right?

907
00:37:20,838 --> 00:37:21,606
There's still the big joker.

908
00:37:21,672 --> 00:37:23,040
I can't bomb three cards.

909
00:37:23,374 --> 00:37:25,009
Then excuse me.

910
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:26,043
It's over.

911
00:37:27,011 --> 00:37:27,845
Over. Completely over.

912
00:37:28,446 --> 00:37:28,913
Xiaofei,

913
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:30,281
hurry and stop Xiao Lin.

914
00:37:31,282 --> 00:37:31,515
King.

915
00:37:32,083 --> 00:37:32,383
Pair.

916
00:37:32,450 --> 00:37:32,783
I pass.

917
00:37:33,684 --> 00:37:34,185
That's right.

918
00:37:36,087 --> 00:37:36,520
Director Zheng.

919
00:37:39,991 --> 00:37:40,825
I pass too.

920
00:37:42,193 --> 00:37:43,160
Pair of eights.

921
00:37:43,327 --> 00:37:44,028
I'm out.

922
00:37:44,629 --> 00:37:44,962
Beautiful.

923
00:37:45,162 --> 00:37:45,663
Excellent.

924
00:37:48,165 --> 00:37:49,000
You also had a pair of jacks.

925
00:37:52,403 --> 00:37:52,970
Xiao Lin,

926
00:37:53,638 --> 00:37:55,273
you split a pair of sixes to play that.

927
00:37:55,273 --> 00:37:55,806
See?

928
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:57,642
You were completely setting up

929
00:37:57,642 --> 00:37:58,309
Old Sheng's big joker.

930
00:37:58,376 --> 00:37:59,277
See?

931
00:37:59,944 --> 00:38:00,811
You two are working together.

932
00:38:01,646 --> 00:38:02,480
You don't look like a beginner.

933
00:38:02,613 --> 00:38:04,148
Exactly, Director Lin.

934
00:38:04,248 --> 00:38:04,749
Pretending to be weak while hiding your strength.

935
00:38:05,983 --> 00:38:07,084
Are we still playing?

936
00:38:07,351 --> 00:38:07,885
Of course.

937
00:38:08,386 --> 00:38:08,919
Come on.

938
00:38:09,153 --> 00:38:10,288
If we lose,

939
00:38:10,588 --> 00:38:11,255
I'll drink.

940
00:38:11,355 --> 00:38:12,189
If we lose this round,

941
00:38:20,798 --> 00:38:21,399
I'll finish a whole bottle.

942
00:38:21,532 --> 00:38:22,199
Thank you.

943
00:38:23,034 --> 00:38:24,035
Sorry.

944
00:38:25,369 --> 00:38:25,970
It's okay.

945
00:38:26,003 --> 00:38:26,971
Come on.

946
00:38:28,239 --> 00:38:29,407
Let's keep playing.

947
00:38:30,107 --> 00:38:32,143
A good cardiac surgeon

948
00:38:32,143 --> 00:38:33,210
is truly hard to find.

949
00:38:36,447 --> 00:38:37,415
We're short-staffed.

950
00:38:38,683 --> 00:38:39,684
After all, Zhang Zhen is gone.

951
00:38:41,752 --> 00:38:42,520
And Ye and the others

952
00:38:43,387 --> 00:38:44,322
still need time to grow.

953
00:38:44,955 --> 00:38:45,990
So for now,

954
00:38:47,291 --> 00:38:48,092
we really have to rely on you.

955
00:38:48,326 --> 00:38:49,193
I understand.

956
00:38:51,095 --> 00:38:51,962
Where else could he go?

957
00:38:52,963 --> 00:38:53,931
Nowhere will take him.

958
00:39:00,404 --> 00:39:01,205
I'm responsible

959
00:39:02,239 --> 00:39:03,174
for what happened to Zhang Zhen.

960
00:39:06,811 --> 00:39:08,279
He followed me

961
00:39:09,680 --> 00:39:10,448
from the day he graduated.

962
00:39:11,282 --> 00:39:12,149
For all these years,

963
00:39:12,717 --> 00:39:13,517
he worked diligently without complaint.

964
00:39:14,351 --> 00:39:15,786
I thought I was looking after him.

965
00:39:19,590 --> 00:39:20,991
But in fact,

966
00:39:22,593 --> 00:39:23,561
I didn't care for him nearly enough.

967
00:39:27,631 --> 00:39:28,999
After I took office,

968
00:39:29,133 --> 00:39:30,668
the department's performance fell.

969
00:39:32,002 --> 00:39:33,237
That's why he went down the wrong path.

970
00:39:34,371 --> 00:39:35,373
Don't blame yourself.

971
00:39:36,407 --> 00:39:37,641
I think what happened

972
00:39:38,142 --> 00:39:39,410
was because he himself

973
00:39:39,443 --> 00:39:40,444
wasn't firm enough.

974
00:39:46,784 --> 00:39:48,185
Can you do me another favor?

975
00:39:49,053 --> 00:39:49,520
Tell me.

976
00:39:50,688 --> 00:39:51,355
Lately,

977
00:39:51,756 --> 00:39:53,324
I've been trying to help Zhang Zhen find a way forward.

978
00:39:54,492 --> 00:39:55,593
But almost everyone I know

979
00:39:56,227 --> 00:39:57,361
is in the medical field,

980
00:39:58,496 --> 00:39:59,330
and to some degree,

981
00:39:59,663 --> 00:40:00,798
they've all heard what happened.

982
00:40:02,066 --> 00:40:02,867
So I'd like you

983
00:40:02,967 --> 00:40:03,601
to advise me.

984
00:40:05,870 --> 00:40:07,238
If he truly can't work as a doctor anymore,

985
00:40:08,639 --> 00:40:09,240
are there

986
00:40:09,273 --> 00:40:10,274
other career paths for him?

987
00:40:10,875 --> 00:40:11,242
All right.

988
00:40:11,876 --> 00:40:12,676
I'll keep this in mind

989
00:40:13,677 --> 00:40:14,745
and treat it seriously.

990
00:40:15,446 --> 00:40:16,414
But don't feel pressured.

991
00:40:19,016 --> 00:40:20,084
This is purely a personal matter.

992
00:40:21,085 --> 00:40:23,053
Then I'll

993
00:40:25,089 --> 00:40:25,923
approach this purely personally

994
00:40:26,791 --> 00:40:28,325
and still treat it seriously.

995
00:40:28,425 --> 00:40:30,027
How about this:

996
00:40:32,797 --> 00:40:33,264
you must be hungry.

997
00:40:35,065 --> 00:40:35,733
I'll buy you a late-night meal.

998
00:40:37,201 --> 00:40:38,068
Can we eat something else?

999
00:40:42,006 --> 00:40:42,907
Director Zhou.

1000
00:40:42,907 --> 00:40:43,441
Sure.

1001
00:40:44,909 --> 00:40:45,309
Something better.

1002
00:40:46,544 --> 00:40:47,344
No problem.

1003
00:40:47,411 --> 00:40:48,045
Didn't you say something good?

1004
00:40:49,814 --> 00:40:50,748
And we're eating this?

1005
00:40:51,148 --> 00:40:51,849
This is exactly what I wanted.

1006
00:40:52,783 --> 00:40:53,717
A familiar taste.

1007
00:40:54,051 --> 00:40:55,152
Thank you.

1008
00:40:56,086 --> 00:40:56,487
Are you nostalgic for overnight shifts?

1009
00:40:58,088 --> 00:40:59,924
That wish is easy to fulfill.

1010
00:41:00,491 --> 00:41:01,826
What I miss is

1011
00:41:02,159 --> 00:41:03,627
the cafeteria cook's

1012
00:41:03,727 --> 00:41:04,695
inconsistent heat control,

1013
00:41:04,829 --> 00:41:05,830
and that sense of mission:

1014
00:41:05,930 --> 00:41:06,430
I had to eat quickly,

1015
00:41:06,463 --> 00:41:08,132
then go back and write charts.

1016
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:11,001
Back when

1017
00:41:12,002 --> 00:41:12,903
I was still doing clinical work,

1018
00:41:13,003 --> 00:41:14,205
I always thought the cafeteria food

1019
00:41:14,238 --> 00:41:15,072
was too basic.

1020
00:41:15,372 --> 00:41:16,006
Now it's different.

1021
00:41:16,407 --> 00:41:18,075
At business dinners, there's fine wine and food,

1022
00:41:18,442 --> 00:41:20,010
but everything tastes like wax

1023
00:41:20,211 --> 00:41:21,111
and I sit there on edge.

1024
00:41:22,079 --> 00:41:23,314
Who said it?

1025
00:41:24,448 --> 00:41:25,816
At a dinner with leaders,

1026
00:41:25,850 --> 00:41:26,717
anyone who actually eats their fill

1027
00:41:26,784 --> 00:41:27,785
has no future.

1028
00:41:29,086 --> 00:41:29,887
Everything I once disliked

1029
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:31,388
has come back like a boomerang.

1030
00:41:32,423 --> 00:41:34,291
Whenever you want it, come here.

1031
00:41:34,725 --> 00:41:36,126
Use my meal card freely.

1032
00:41:37,127 --> 00:41:38,529
How generous, Director Zhou.

1033
00:41:39,563 --> 00:41:40,397
I have to toast you.

1034
00:41:42,967 --> 00:41:43,434
You're too kind.

1035
00:42:23,507 --> 00:42:25,075
Do you know what time it is?

1036
00:42:26,110 --> 00:42:27,678
Hurry up, wash, and go to sleep.
